@startuml
actor Penjual
actor Pembeli
boundary View
control OrderController
entity OrderModel
database Database

Penjual -> View: Buka Daftar Pesanan Masuk (Dibayar)
Penjual -> View: Klik "Proses Pesanan"
View -> OrderController: POST /seller/orders/{id}/process
OrderController -> OrderModel: processOrder()
OrderModel -> Database: UPDATE orders
OrderController --> View: Refresh Daftar

Penjual -> View: Siapkan Barang & Input Resi Pengiriman
View -> OrderController: POST /seller/orders/{id}/ship
OrderController -> OrderModel: shipOrder(tracking_number=resi)
OrderModel -> Database: UPDATE orders
OrderController -> OrderController: Trigger Notification (Mail/DB)
OrderController --> View: Refresh Daftar Pesanan
OrderController --> Pembeli: Kirim Notifikasi (Email: Barang Dikirim)
@enduml